Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:06.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我开门见山地问了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:17.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,请听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,拜托了  我们一起…乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,阻止她
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:38.83,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:38.83,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的这份躁动  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.59,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.59,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像将脸埋入刚洗过的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:53.72,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:53.72,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鸟儿们吟唱着  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:04.78,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:04.78,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论走到哪  这道路都会延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:13.88,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:13.88,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牵手  更像是紧握这手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.65,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.65,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.01,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.01,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空为毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:31.25,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:31.25,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌对面的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:39.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:39.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}为你指向尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:49.20,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:49.20,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才该说谢谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:05.02,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1279.333,915.467)}生命之花仰望鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,请详细说明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:08.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,为了治疗这病  我们去了各种各样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:13.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是日子一天天过去却没有任何线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:15.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,在某个边境之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们遇到了一个占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个占卜师看着我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,是血被玷污之人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:33.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,若不净化这血液  你便无永无安宁之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,污秽之血会以新的血液得以净化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊应该还记得那个占卜师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此将索玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,有了你的血  说不定海特拉就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:36.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,我都约好要永远和爸爸在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:52.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.63,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,乖乖听话  不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,同时他也是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,我完全找不到治疗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类的病谁都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,也不能和别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是海特拉的身体却越来越差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,我以为只要喝下健康人类的血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,说不定他的病就能好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,身体有没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,没有  只是稍微湿了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,等下  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以不要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,擦下头发  不然会着凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,我只能依靠些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算伤害别人  就算背上罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算如此只要是为了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明你就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明想永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我却没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没能做到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,还冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,不冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊真是爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个  真的对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,你做我朋友就原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆先生  关于乌佐伊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  我已经没有追责的打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,对于恋人来讲这是理所当然的行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,我将其理解为家人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没有作为乌佐伊家人的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你不觉得很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,从身为人类的我皮肤上长出来的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,与乌佐伊的眼睛周围和身体上长出来的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃了乌佐伊的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,曾经我和为数不多几位人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,为了躲避异形  四处躲藏求生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,和我最重要的家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:06.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,有一天村子突然被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,是异形们的人类狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,同伴们  女儿的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,都接二连三被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,若是反抗手臂就会被撕毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,想要逃跑就会被扭下双腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:55.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,其中还有被当场吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,总算逃到森林洞窟里的我们还算幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  想到之后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,或许这不应称为幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:38.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为害怕不知何时会到来的异形  精神饱受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,夜晚也不能好好入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,没有像样的食物和水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,就这样过了两天  三天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:51.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,亲爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们三个都到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去看看外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,异形…就在这么近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们也得变得和他们一样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,不变成背离人道的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,就活不下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,老…公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,好疼啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:37.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我没有资格成为她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,至今为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直被欺骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,风变得更强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,说不定会变得狂暴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们稍微绕一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:16.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,转西边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊你的那份早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,我没食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,昨天夜晚里发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:39.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,真不知道该说你是迟钝还是机敏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽你有被欺骗过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,欺骗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  就是欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是一个让一直以来的美好的回忆都变成虚妄的残酷谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我真是太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直被欺骗着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为谎言成为的父女  无法成为真正的父女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为乌佐伊和索玛丽都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,突然发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,是龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样下去会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:27.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,所有人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:36.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉你也会被卷走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在去也只会引起二次灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,我已经确认了被卷走的方向和风的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,从地形上来看  两人平安无事的概率很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,风停后马上去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,嘴里都是沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:35.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:43.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,你刚才说因为谎言成为的家人不是真正的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,但这份喜欢的情感却不是假的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽喜欢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊喜欢海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,参照索玛丽他们的体重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,和风的强度和方向的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,她们两个人应该在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:19.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊或许是听到了昨天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直欺骗着乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,再也无法像以前一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  审判的时刻来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,审判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,对自己曾经犯下的罪行进行审判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,无论结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,必须直面所需要赎罪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使那样会背负更深罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:01.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,是影足鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:20.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,地盘意识很强烈  性情极具攻击性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是冒然接近不仅我们会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,也会连累索玛丽她们受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去引开那只鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,以哥雷姆的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算被攻击到了也能够抵抗住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,趁这个时候  海特拉你去救出乌佐伊她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我先观察时机然后发射闪光弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,那只鸟在慌乱后撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:48.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么  什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉  诱导的任务本应是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样的话更加靠谱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的命已经不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉他打算赴死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,与乌佐伊相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直否定着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,每当她的笑颜和深情的爱对向我时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:47.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的内心深处都在呼喊着  我没有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的救赎只能是拼上自己的性命去保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们两个都闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要擅自一个人结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,你要是选择死亡逃避的话我绝对不会原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么要一直待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就没想如果我知道了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会杀掉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是为你而存在的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果乌佐伊你愿意的话  随时都能够献上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,对  就在此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,那你就给我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:05.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要想用死来赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使多么苦痛也要站起来走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:18.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,然后和我一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就是对你的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我向你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,乌佐伊果然真是个爱哭鬼
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比较着并排的影子相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕阳甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘风而去的是那小小的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什么是永远  什么是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道当我抬头仰望你时  你的侧脸总是那么地闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牵着手传递的这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论何时都在给予我爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}这不断溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到传达到给你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向着共同许下的诺言和未来  前进吧
